one of the largest black sororities in the nation stepped up to help give men, women, boys, girls the courage to step off the diving board and into the water.\", \"from\": 144, \"to\": 383, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 183, \"end\": 188, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sigma\", \"score\": 0.9995338677923933, \"rank\": 0.0004663393583316981, \"text\": \"Sigma\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sigma\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sigma\"}, {\"begin\": 208, \"end\": 223, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sigma_Gamma_Rho\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sigma Gamma Rho\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sigma_Gamma_Rho\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sigma_Gamma_Rho\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Yes, it's about learning to swim, it's also about finding the next Olympic swimmer,\\\" said Maritza McClendon.\", \"from\": 385, \"to\": 494, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 476, \"end\": 483, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maritsa\", \"score\": 0.9317264576154206, \"rank\": 0.0732763804510221, \"text\": \"Maritza\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maritsa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maritsa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Well, they will be standing right next to Maritza McClendon, not only was she the guest instructor at the free national event co-sponsored by the U.S. swimming, she's a decorated Olympian and a history maker.\", \"from\": 496, \"to\": 704, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 538, \"end\": 545, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maritsa\", \"score\": 0.9317264576154206, \"rank\": 0.0732763804510221, \"text\": \"Maritza\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maritsa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maritsa\"}, {\"begin\": 675, \"end\": 683, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999998458445253, \"rank\": 1.528355766385485e-07, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She's the first black woman to make it on the nation's Olympic swim team took home sliver in Athens back in 2004.\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 819, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 799, \"end\": 805, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2004_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9189818709052104, \"rank\": 0.08816072306323407, \"text\": \"Athens\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2004_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2004_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For her, it's not just a profession, it's personal.\", \"from\": 821, \"to\": 872, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If you do not know, 64 percent of African-American children do not know how to swim; and 45 percent of Hispanic children do not know how to swim,\\\" explained McClendon.\", \"from\": 874, \"to\": 1042, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 909, \"end\": 925, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/African_Americans\", \"score\": 0.9999990630962953, \"rank\": 9.367181973046332e-07, \"text\": \"African-American\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/African_Americans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/African_Americans\"}, {\"begin\": 978, \"end\": 986, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hispanic_and_Latino_Americans\", \"score\": 0.8004853782987646, \"rank\": 0.24924205626307136, \"text\": \"Hispanic\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hispanic_and_Latino_Americans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hispanic_and_Latino_Americans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So, it's really important to introduce them to the education as to why we do water safety.\\\"\", \"from\": 1043, \"to\": 1135, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a lesson, Yocelyn Melendez wants for her kids.\", \"from\": 1137, \"to\": 1188, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not know how to swim and it's affected my life negatively so I really want them to learn how to swim,\\\" expressed Melendez.\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1318, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is a lot of open lakes and rivers that we like to go to, but they can not swim, so thankfully with this they will be able to learn at least the basics of how to swim or how to save themselves.\\\"\", \"from\": 1319, \"to\": 1519, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It goes beyond the teaching, there is also a push for these young ones to dream.\", \"from\": 1521, \"to\": 1601, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was that little girl, who did not know how to swim, watched the Olympics and watched them get their medal put on them and hear the star-spangled-banner and I was immediately inspired so that what we are trying to do,\\\" added McClendon.\", \"from\": 1603, \"to\": 1840, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Copyright 2024.\", \"from\": 1842, \"to\": 1857, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Western Mass News (WGGB/WSHM).\", \"from\": 1858, \"to\": 1888, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1858, \"end\": 1865, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Western_world\", \"score\": 0.9601856109592692, \"rank\": 0.024850708839495333, \"text\": \"Western\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Western_world\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Western_world\"}, {\"begin\": 1866, \"end\": 1870, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mass_in_the_Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 0.9941389262281882, \"rank\": 0.0058321704389068425, \"text\": \"Mass\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mass_in_the_Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mass_in_the_Catholic_Church\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 1909, \"entities\": []}]}"